X_{1},...,X_{30}
 P(25 \le \sum_{i=1}^{30}X_{i} \le 35) 
 \bar{X}_{30} = \frac{1}{30}\sum_{i=1}^{30}X_{i} 
 P(25 \le \sum_{i=1}^{30}X_{i} \le 35) = P(\frac{25}{30} \le \bar{X}_{30} \le \frac{35}{30}) \ge 1 - \frac{V(\bar{X}_{30})}{(5/30)^{2}} 
\frac{25}{30} = 1 - 5/30
\frac{35}{30} = 1 + 5/30
V(\bar{X}_{30}) = \sigma^{2}/30
\sigma = 1
